(80320, 'To Captain Snowbeard.\n\nThe supplylines between Ironforge and Menethil harbor is being strained every day, caravans are being attacked by the Dragonmaw Orc and even getting to you has become a hassle between them, and the aggresive wildlife.', 80321),
